1. Create a warehouse which can store products
2. The warehouse has limit on the number of products it can produce
3. products can be added or removed from warehouse
4. the warehouse keeps track of count of products available, available spoace and capacity
5. 2 types of products - gadget and widget
6. they both have title and price
7. gadget is sold in packs
8. widget has an expiry date after which its value become zero
9. the warehouse can get us total value of all products in warehouse
10. trying to add new product to warehouse which does not exist throws an exception
11. trying to remove product from warehouse  which does not exist throws an exception
12. Trying to create an impossible warehouse of negative capacity throws an exception